snippet.title: Fortune Decker [Gameplay]
snippet.description:
Fortune Decker is a top-down roguelike, deckbuilding, action survival game being developed by Evil Kiwi Games.

ABOUT [FORTUNE DECKER 🔮🃏✨]
Prototype available (FREE) on itch.io: https://ismerrn.itch.io/fortune-decker
Webpage (press kit, one-liner, gameplay, and more) : https://fortunedecker.carrd.co
